  <title>建立连接</title>

  <p>You can connect to other computers on your local network using
  <app>Remote Desktop Viewer</app>.</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>选择 <guiseq><gui style="menu">远程</gui> <gui style="menuitem">连接</gui></guiseq>。</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>为连接选择<gui>协议</gui>和<gui>主机</gui>。</p>
      <note>
        <p>某些协议允许您通过点击<gui style="button">查找</gui>按钮来查看局域网中所有的计算机。若没有<app>avahi</app>支持，该按钮将不会显示。</p>
      </note>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>选择连接建立时您要启用的选项。选项会根据您使用的协议变化。</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>点击<gui style="button">连接</gui>按钮。</p>
      <p>此时，远程桌面可能需要确认连接。如果是这样，查看器可能会在连接确认前变黑。</p>
      <note>
        <p>Some computers may require a secure connection: an authentication
        dialog will be displayed, asking for the credentials. The type of
        credentials depend on the remote host; it may be a password and a
        username. If you select <gui>Remember this credential</gui>,
        <app>Remote Desktop Viewer</app> will store the information using
        <app>GNOME Keyring</app>.</p>
      </note>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <p>如果连接原先使用过，您也可以通过<guiseq><gui style="menu">远程</gui><gui style="menuitem">最近连接</gui></guiseq>来启用它。</p>

  <p>要关闭连接，选择 <guiseq><gui style="menu">远程</gui> <gui style="menuitem">关闭</gui></guiseq> 或点击 <gui style="button">关闭</gui> 按钮。</p>

